title: 🌟3 bed + Office (or 4th bed) - HUGE Yard & Garage Parking🌟
posting_body: ['SUMMARY:', 'Clean, well-kept 3 bed + Office (or 4th bedroom) / 2 bath upper unit duplex located in a peaceful neighborhood, with a HUGE fenced-in backyard, 2 garage parking spots and 2 off-street parking spots.', 'Walkable to all the great bars and restaurants Eat Street and Lyn-Lake have to offer!', 'Details for how to book a tour are at the end of this post, so please keep reading.', 'ABOUT THE PROPERTY:', '3 bedroom + Office (or 4th bedroom), 2 bathroom upper unit of a duplex', 'Available September 1st', 'Rent: $2,400/month', 'Tenants responsible for Electric, Gas, Cable/Internet', 'Full AC and Heat', 'Washer and Dryer in basement', 'Quiet street', 'Easy access to Lake of the Isles, Loring Park, Downtown, Eat Street, and Lyn-Lake', '2 Garage Parking Spots available for $50/month', '2 Off-Street Parking Spots available for $30/month', 'Pets are negotiable', 'MINIMUM QUALIFICATIONS:', 'Pass credit and background check', 'NO SMOKERS', 'No prior evictions', 'Gross monthly income must be 3x the rent', 'Credit score of AT LEAST 620', 'HOW TO BOOK A TOUR:', 'copy and paste the following google form into your browser, complete the questions, and I will contact you: https://forms.gle/5ERASjhmS8QGkYo38']
